sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    
    participant Client as Cliente (Web/Mobile)
    participant API as API Gateway / Nginx
    participant App as Laravel SaaS Core
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (SaaS)
    participant Redis as Cache / Queues
    
    Client->>API: Solicitud (Bearer Token)
    API->>App: Forward Request
    
    activate App
    App->>App: IdentifyTenant (Middleware)
    
    App->>Redis: Check Cache (Rate Limiting)
    Redis-->>App: OK
    
    App->>DB: Query Data (Tenant Isolated)
    activate DB
    DB-->>App: Dataset
    deactivate DB
    
    App->>App: Transform Resource
    App-->>Client: JSON Response (200 OK)
    deactivate App
